<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Aadhaar Verification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f6f8;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      margin: 50px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777777;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Aadhaar Verification Required</h2>
    <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
    <p>To complete your KYC process, please verify your Aadhaar by clicking the button below:</p>
    
    <a href="<%= verificationLink %>" class="btn">Verify Aadhaar</a>

    <p>If the button above does not work, please copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
    <p><%= verificationLink %></p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
